{"name": "odoo11-addon-account-tax-balance", "metadata": {"name": "odoo11-addon-account-tax-balance", "version": "11.0.1.0.0", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://www.agilebg.com/", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo", "odoo11-addon-date-range"], "summary": "Compute tax balances based on date range", "upload_time": 1510637412}, "documentation": ["```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.svg\n:alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n:target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n```\n\n# Tax Balances\n\nThis module allows to compute tax balances within a certain date range.\nIt depends on date_range module and exposes 'compute' methods that can be called by other modules (like localization ones)\n\n## Usage\n\nAccounting --> Reporting --> Taxes Balance\n\nSelect the company, the date range, the target moves and 'open taxes'\n\n:::{figure} /account_tax_balance/static/description/tax_balance.png\n:::\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/website/image/ir.attachment/5784_f2813bd/datas\n:alt: Try me on Runbot\n:target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/91/11.0\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/account-financial-reporting/issues). In case of trouble, please\ncheck there if your issue has already been reported. If you spotted it first,\nhelp us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed feedback.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Images\n\n- Odoo Community Association: [Icon](https://github.com/OCA/maintainer-tools/blob/master/template/module/static/description/icon.svg).\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Lorenzo Battistini \\<<mailto:lorenzo.battistini@agilebg.com>>\n- Giovanni Capalbo \\<<mailto:giovanni@therp.nl>>\n- Tecnativa - Antonio Espinosa\n- Tecnativa - Pedro M. Baeza\n- ACSONE SA/NV - St\u00e9phane Bidoul\n\n### Maintainer\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nTo contribute to this module, please visit <https://odoo-community.org>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_tax_balance.wizard", "documentation": ["-*- coding: utf-8 -*-", "\u00a9 2016 Lorenzo Battistini - Agile Business Group", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_tax_balance.wizard.open_tax_balances", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_tax_balance.wizard..open_tax_balances", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_tax_balance.wizard.open_tax_balances", "documentation": ["-*- coding: utf-8 -*-", "\u00a9 2016 Lorenzo Battistini - Agile Business Group", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_tax_balance.wizard.open_tax_balances.OpenTaxBalances", "bases": ["models.TransientModel"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_tax_balance.wizard.open_tax_balances.OpenTaxBalances.onchange_date_range_id", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_tax_balance.wizard.open_tax_balances.OpenTaxBalances.open_taxes", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_tax_balance.wizard.open_tax_balances.OpenTaxBalances._name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_tax_balance.wizard.open_tax_balances.OpenTaxBalances.company_id", "type": null, "docume